    ABOUT US

    We are team MAKSAT ( a Hindi word which means aim in English). As our name suggests, MAKSAT aims to make this country a better place for its citizens and the future generations. We engage ourselves in charitable and philanthropic work  because we care about our citizens and the environment that they inhabit. we believe in making world, a safe space for everyone from all walks of life to dwell in. we truly go by living for the people, by the people and to the people
